# Public root for the self-managed nachweis demo WRPRC-provider trust bundle.
# The WRPRC-provider signing key is a DIFFERENT actor from the WRPAC CA (ETSI TS 119 475:
# registrar, WRPAC provider, and WRPRC provider are distinct), and its private key remains
# offline, provisioned by Workstream A. Until the public provider anchor is published here this
# file is intentionally empty of certificates, so WRPRC verification fails closed.
